high_descs: Turn around and go to the bed.
Pick up the phone from the bed.
Turn right and go to the dresser.
Put the phone on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move the phone from the bed to the dresser.

high_descs: Turn around completely and walk to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the cell phone that is on the bed.
Turn to your right and move forward towards the dresser.
Place the phone upright in a vertical position on top of the CD that is on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move a phone from the bed to the dresser.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then right again to face the end of the bed.
Pick the phone up from the bed.
Turn to the right and face the dresser.
Put the phone down on the dresser on top of the disc.
anns.task_desc: Put a phone on a dresser.
